name: Senior #30 - Gertrude
description:
Gertrude a.k.a The Rave Grandma is a 88-year-old internet sensation who enjoys long acid trips, shuffle dancing to ‘Wade - No Logic’, and baking space cakes. She is extremely fun and pleasant to be with, but can also be chaotic and out of control.

She is a widower who defines herself as queer. Her grandson Benji, who also has a mullet haircut, helps her sell her merchandise online and is in charge of dealing with the media and clients.
